rComments: Very caring and smart. She's funny and gets to know her students well. Not a hard marker I would say fair and totally possible to get an A. She is very refreshing and easy to understand in lectures. I really enjoyed the class. One page of writing a week tho but not hard writing mostly. She is also very understanding & answers emails. I recommend.
Absolutely amazing prof!! She truly cares about all her students and is very enthusiastic when she teaches. A real gem of a prof at uOttawa.
